          <h2>
           <a href="http://one.arch.tamu.edu/news/2018/11/8/planning-prof-notes-cities-post-harvey-planning-changes/">
            Planning prof notes post-Harvey city planning changes
           </a>
          </h2>
          <div class="publication-date">
           <span>
            posted
           </span>
           Thu, 08 Nov 2018
          </div>
          <div class="description">
           Hurricane Harvey’s widespread damage forced cities throughout the U.S. to take a more critical look at their infrastructure and hazard mitigation plans, said Galen Newman, Texas A&amp;M associate professor of urban planning.
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
