          <h2>
           <a href="http://one.arch.tamu.edu/news/2018/3/19/sea-grant-collaboration/">
            TAMU agencies unite to help build resilient coastal communities
           </a>
          </h2>
          <div class="publication-date">
           <span>
            posted
           </span>
           Mon, 19 Mar 2018
          </div>
          <div class="description">
           In the wake of Hurricane Harvey, two Texas A&amp;M groups have teamed up to launch the Community Resilience Collaborative, a program aimed at bolstering the resilience of the state’s coastal communities to natural hazards and at restoring their habitats and ecosystems.
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
